Business Brief -- Property Trust of America:
   REIT Purchases Apartments
   In Arizona for $17 Million
Separately, Property Trust said it registered with the
Securities and Exchange Commission to offer 6.3 million
additional shares. The company said five million of the
shares will be offered through an underwriting team led by
Merrill Lynch  Co. In addition, 1.3 million shares will be
offered to the company's largest shareholder, Southwest
Realty Advisors Inc., which is controlled by William D.
Sanders, and its owners. Southwest Realty owns about 22.6% of
Property Trust's approximately 13.2 million shares
outstanding.